Pink Floyd
On The Turning Away Live (Solo)
Delicate Sound Of Thunder

Notation:
b(17) = bend to appropriate tone, ex. 17th fret
r(15) = release bend to appropriate tone, ex. 15th fret
15b(17)r(15) = bend string at 15th fret to get 17th fret tone then
release bend from 17th fret tone to 15th
p = pull off
h = hammer on
AH = artificial harmonic

Note: Not to time; vibrato left out, listen to recording for appropriate timing and 
vibrato / whammy bar use.

